'''麥哲倫橋'''（Magellanic Bridge）是連接大小[[麥哲倫雲|麥哲倫雲]]的一條由中性[[氫|氫]]組成的氣流<ref name="putn">{{cite journal|title=The Magellanic System's Interactive Formations|url=http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/full/2000PASA...17....1P%26data_type%3DPDF_HIGH%26whole_paper%3DYES%26type%3DPRINTER%26filetype%3D.pdf|first1=M. E.|journal=Publications of the Astronomical Society of Australia|issue=|doi=10.1071/AS00001|year=2013|volume=17|page=1|format=Free PDF download|bibcode=2000PASA...17....1P|last1=Putman|access-date=2014-02-20|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305030216/http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/full/2000PASA...17....1P%26data_type%3DPDF_HIGH%26whole_paper%3DYES%26type%3DPRINTER%26filetype%3D.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它的特徵是氣體的[[金屬量|金屬量]]很低，並且僅曾在其中發現少量的[[恆星|恆星]]<ref name="lehner">{{Cite journal|title=FUSE Observations of the Magellanic Bridge|url=https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2001AAS...199.6506L/abstract|last=Lehner|first=N.|date=2001-12|journal=American Astronomical Society Meeting Abstracts|volume=199|pages=65.06|language=en|access-date=2020-07-14|archive-date=2020-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200313084848/https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2001AAS...199.6506L/abstract|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Lehner, NNicolas "[http://arxiv.org/pdf/astro-ph/0206250.pdf FUSE Observations of the Magellanic Bridge Gas toward Two Early-Type Stars: Molecules, Physical Conditions, and Relative Abundance] {{Wayback|url=http://arxiv.org/pdf/astro-ph/0206250.pdf |date=20191215223539 }}." arXiv preprint astro-ph/0206250 (2002)</ref>。不要將它與[[麥哲倫星流|麥哲倫星流]]混淆在一起，後者將麥哲倫雲與[[銀河系|銀河系]]連結在一起，是[[J._V._Hindman|J. V. Hindman]]等人在1963年發現的<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Magellanic Bridge: The Nearest Purely Tidal Stellar Population|url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/511816/meta|last=Harris|first=Jason|date=2007-03-20|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|issue=1|doi=10.1086/511816|volume=658|pages=345|language=en|issn=0004-637X}}</ref>。

